Description: Tier 3 spell
                 Targets: N/A
		 Creates an invisible 'trap' in the room from which the
		 caster conjures this spell. For a moderate duration of
		 time, the caster will be notified of anyone that passes
		 through the room (reporting the short description of
		 passerby). 
		 
